msgid "# triton.language.multibuffer"
msgstr "# triton.language.multibuffer"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/multibuffer.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/multibuffer.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：为张量设置多缓冲，允许编译器对同一张量创建多个副本。\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Set multiple buffers for a tensor, allowing the compiler to create multiple copies of the same tensor.\n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/multibuffer.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.multibuffer(\n"
"    src,\n"
"    size,\n"
"    _builder=None\n"
") -> None\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/multibuffer.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/multibuffer.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/multibuffer.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `src`        | `tensor`          | 需要进行多缓冲设置的源张量                                                     |\n"
"| `size`       | `int` 或 `constexpr`    | 要创建的缓冲区副本数量                                                        |\n"
"| `_builder` |- | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                            |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type               | Description                                                      |\n"
"| ------------- | ------------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `src`         | `tensor`           | The source tensor for which multi-buffer setup is required       |\n"
"| `size`        | `int` or `constexpr` | Number of buffer copies to create                                |\n"
"| `_builder`    | -                  | Reserved parameter, external calls are not supported for now     |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/multibuffer.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`None`：此操作为一个编译提示，不会在运行时返回值，仅影响编译器的优化行为。\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`None`: This operation is a compilation hint that does not return a value at runtime and only affects the compiler's optimization behavior.\n"

